Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你怎么这么紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上了哦  我合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐  这样好难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢  哎呀～十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  忧能够合格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样也无法埋没在场诸位的功劳…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子合格了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯看上去反倒更高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糊涂妈妈？不  糊涂姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个温暖又幸福的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又分在一起了呢
