Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和良子能一个班级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  二年二班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我也是二班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这么说  难道小澪也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…一班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛  那个眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得寂寞了随时可以过来玩哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当我是小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  倒是律你离开了我没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能给你看作业了哦
