Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里可是有在哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合适很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新气十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  领子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣店的标签还粘着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你最近睡觉头发都乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要再起早一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如调换一下姐姐和妹妹位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  二班是在二楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有高年级学生的感觉啊
