Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又分在一起了呢
