Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个认识的都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和唯分到不同的班级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在担心有没有认识的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是今年还请多…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:12.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：「新生欢迎会」的意思。\N由于汉语的「新欢」太有喜感，于是就这样用啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加入篮球部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎加入超自然研
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对乒乓球有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  已经人山人海了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大社团的排场就是不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别拿轻音部不当部看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  传单呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑…姑且算是做了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感觉好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句话  没卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  轻音部的卖点是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  比如茶水点心任凭享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了睡睡了吃的轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个貌似不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有啥别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可缺乏冲击力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话就去创造吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有新生欢迎演出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要来看喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣的同学欢迎放学后来音乐准备室汪汪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有好多好吃的点心哦～咯咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…是不是起反作用了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以加入什么社团好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣的话  放学后请务必来三楼的音乐准备室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跑过去是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这也太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？像打工一样好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真喜欢打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光在那里辛苦  却没什么人接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在明天的演出上扳回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我还做了这套衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  下午的课开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去轻音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有种很帅的感觉呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我就算了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  爵士乐研在二楼的社团教室有说明会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是小忧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你要加入轻音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连律和都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  让一下行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很欢迎哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前  刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该是在超自然研的旁边的旁边…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊啊啊啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得应该是音乐教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐室…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从圣诞节之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和老师给大家换衣服换上瘾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我姐姐唯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫平泽唯  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就给你上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个拿过去就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫的  小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就坐着吧  剩下的我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是部长田井中律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个潇洒的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又没交讲堂的使用申请书对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的演出会演不成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要说几遍才知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是琴吹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么吵闹真是不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是个温柔的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  这身打扮算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  秋山澪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常害羞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢  澪  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲在那里  快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  你们会笑我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会笑啊  很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子老师  轻音部的顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来穿穿吗～？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真正的爵士乐有点差距啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  样子好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算像个轻音部的模样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  我吊带卡在肩膀处了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…下摆真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖子…啊  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  太不方便啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说要穿女仆装演奏的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是换成运动衫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  开始吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一位  选手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥呢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好帅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好帅但是这运动衫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些穿玩偶套装的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看一眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动衫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个不是平泽同学吗？和咱们同班的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很困扰的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是个认真活动的社团吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有好好给你们表演  真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是挺认真地练习来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之明天的Live要表演4首  一定要来听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请投上您公正的一票
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我们差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我就先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…很多方面都挺强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…我去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这看来是没希望了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…她说你们挺强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧～  明天也会来看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦～轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部最好的地方是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是会让人觉得很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是乐在其中嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧你要不要也一起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是武道馆演唱会！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来姐姐自从加入轻音部之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也变得生龙活虎起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧～冰淇淋～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：谁来收掉这条虫=_,=||）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在完全一头扎进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃冰淇淋～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然也有没变的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…小气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是新生欢迎会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但但但但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是在紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里捡到了一百日元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你给我再紧张一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「软软呼呼Time」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咖喱后米饭」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的爱是订书机」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「毛笔与圆珠笔」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪的特色别人还真是学不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  主唱全部让我来好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来的确还没定好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  难得两个人都能唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪你也来唱一首如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  拍个手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！我绝对不唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但上次演出反响很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再出那样的意外事故啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拉面的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得配饺子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的抵触心理啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就全让唯来唱算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是轻音乐部的社团介绍和演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  我就只说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:16:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服也出乎意料地出彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…请快到舞台侧厅去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你已经决定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  爵士乐研究会有个很帅的前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想加入什么社团也是个人自由嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  硬拉你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人还真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐原来是主唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  首先祝贺各位新生入学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次听说轻音部时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是「很轻松的音乐」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯的演唱发言能叫人安下心来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就抱着\N「会敲响板大概就可以了吧」的心态加入社团了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  也请大家抱着这样轻松的心态加入社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「响板其实也挺难的」  小佐和老师这么讲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  「小佐和」其实是音乐老师的外号…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想搞小品音乐吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我的爱是订书机」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开头的riff挺难的  可她却一点走音都没有  但是…
